Package: charm
Type: Package
Title: Analysis of DNA methylation data from CHARM microarrays
Version: 0.99.0
Date: 2010-02-10
Author: Martin Aryee, Peter Murakami, Srinivasan Yegnasubramanian, Rafael Irizarry
Maintainer: Martin Aryee <aryee@jhu.edu>
Depends: R(>= 2.10.0), Biobase, oligo, oligoClasses, SQN, fields
Imports: preprocessCore, methods, stats, Biostrings, IRanges,  siggenes, gtools
Suggests: charmData, BSgenome.Hsapiens.UCSC.hg18
Description: This package implements analysis tools for DNA methylation microarrays. It finds differentially methylated regions between samples, calculates percentage methylation estimates and includes array quality assessment tools.
License: LGPL (>= 2)
LazyLoad: yes
biocViews: Microarray, Bioinformatics
